{
  "id": "adv_main_02_14_03",
  "title": "東京編2章43話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――第一回I-UNITY、そのファイナルから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One month after the final round",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一ヶ月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "of the first I-UNITY",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、準備出来たか？\nそれじゃあ、I-UNITYの表彰式に向かおうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone ready?\nShall we head to the I-UNITY awards ceremony?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n楽しみだな～。一ヶ月も待っちゃったからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nI’m so excited~. We’ve been waiting for a whole month.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "大会の後にいろんなことがあったから\n延期は仕方なかったとは思うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A lot has happened since the tournament‚\nso I think it was unavoidable that it was postponed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "ステージに立ってたみなさんとしては\n全然終わった気がしませんでしたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But for those of you who were on stage‚\nit must’ve felt like it never really ended‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、このひと月でいろんなことがあったな\n例えば……姫野さんの逮捕と、朝倉さんの釈放かな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right‚ a lot has happened in the past month.\nFor example… Himeno-san’s arrest and Asakura-san’s release.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんの集めていた証拠が\n決め手になったんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The evidence that Saegusa-san gathered\nwas the deciding factor‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう。バンプロでの資金の横領やその偽造が暴かれた\n余罪がないか、今なお警察は躍起になってるって話だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. The embezzlement and forgery at Van Prods. were exposed‚\nand I heard the police are still working hard to see if there are any other offenses.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで朝倉さんも\n無事に戻ってこられたんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to that‚ Asakura-san\nwas able to come back safe and sound.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.11,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、凄くホッとしてたよね！\nあまり顔には出てなかったけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui must’ve been so relieved!\nEven though she didn’t really show it on her face!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.01,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、姫野さんは本当に、もう……！\nファイナルではスタッフを買収してまで、ライブを妨害",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But still‚ Himeno-san‚ honestly‚ ugh……!\nIn the final‚ she went as far as bribing the staff to sabotage the live‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 67.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "目的のためにはアイドルの夢をぞんざいに扱う……\nそんなの絶対に許せませんよ！　ふんす！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "trampling on the dreams of idols for her own selfish goals…\nThat’s absolutely unforgivable! Hmph!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁまぁ、さとみさん\nけが人とかは出ませんでしたし、もう過ぎたことですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-calm down‚ Satomi-san.\nNo one got hurt‚ and it’s all in the past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、ああいう状況でも\n最後までライブをやりきれて満足出来てますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even in that situation‚\nwe were able to complete our performance and were satisfied with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "うう……川咲さんは優し過ぎます！\nその優しさはむしろギルティーですよ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh……Sakura-san‚ you’re too kind!\nYour kindness is almost a sin~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 103.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 103.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 103.4
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 103.4666666702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、延期とはいえ\nここまで時間がかかるとは思いませんでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I didn’t think\nit would take this long.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 110.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……主宰者の中核である姫野さんの不正が\nどこまで及んでいたか分からなかったからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… We didn’t know\nhow far Himeno-san’s corruption reached.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテはもちろん、他の事務所にも疑惑が\nかけられて、調べ尽くすしかなかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pret-a-Porter was under suspicion‚ of course‚ but so were the other agencies‚\nso we had no choice but to investigate everything thoroughly……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 124.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "健全な審査のもとで結果が出されていた\nってことが証明出来ないと、表彰も何もないですしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We had to prove that the results were determined\nthrough fair judging‚ or else we couldn’t hold the awards ceremony.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 132.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんと朝倉さんには、感謝しないとですね\n立て直しのために、凄く忙しそうにしてたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to thank Saegusa-san and Asakura-san.\nThey’ve been so busy trying to get their agencies back on track.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。一時はそのまま\n三枝さんが協会の理事になるのか？　とも思ったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. For a while‚ I thought\nSaegusa-san would be the chairman of the association‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 148.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-stm006.m4a",
      "text": "蹴ったって聞きましたよ、朝倉さんに譲るからって\nせっかくのポストなのに……社長って変わってますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I heard he turned it down. He said he’d give the position to Asakura-san.\nHe gave up such a prestigious position…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 158.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんはまだちゃんと会ったことがないんだもんね\n三枝さんは……まぁ、そういう人なんだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You haven’t really met Asakura-san yet‚ Satomi-san.\nSaegusa-san is… well‚ that’s just how he is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 167.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、朝倉さんが戻って来たってことは\nバンプロも復活するんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ now that Asakura-san’s back‚\nthat means Van Prods. will be back in business‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことになるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that’s right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 176.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
